* {{ill|Dairizuka Kofun Cluster|ja|内裏塚古墳群|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Futtsu, Chiba|ja|富津市|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Chiba Prefecture|ja|千葉県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}})
* {{ill|Anesaki Futagozuka Kofun|lt=Anegasaki Kofun Cluster|ja|姉崎古墳群|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Ichihara, Chiba|ja|市原市|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Chiba Prefecture|ja|千葉県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}})
* {{ill|Isohama Kofun Cluster|ja|磯浜古墳群|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Ōarai, Ibaraki|ja|東茨城郡大洗町|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Ibaraki Prefecture|ja|茨城県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}})
