]) * [[:en:Goshikizuka (Sentsubo) Kofun|Goshikizuka Kofun]] ({{ill|Tarumi-ku, Kobe|ja|神戸市垂水区|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tarumi-ku, Kobe|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, [[:en:Hyōgo Prefecture|Hyōgo Prefecture]]) * [[:en:Amino Chōshiyama Kofun|Amino Chōshiyama Kofun]] ([[:en:Kyōtango|Kyōtango]], [[:en:Kyoto Prefecture|Kyoto Prefecture]]) * [[:en:Nagae-Sakurayama Kofun Cluster|Nagae-Sakurayama Kofun Cluster]] ([[:en:Zushi, Kanagawa|Zushi, Kanagawa]] / {{ill|Hayama, Kanagawa|ja|三浦郡葉山町|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hayama, Kanagawa|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, [[:en:Kanagawa Prefecture|Kanagawa Prefecture]]) * {{ill|Dairizuka Kofun Cluster|ja|内裏塚古墳群|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dairizuka Kofun Cluster|qq=}} ([[:en:Futtsu|Futtsu, Chiba]], [[:en:Chiba Prefecture|Chiba Prefecture]]) * {{ill|Anesaki Futagozuka Kofun|lt=Anegasaki Kofun Cluster|ja|姉崎古墳群|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Anesaki Futagozuka Kofun|qq=}} ([[:en:Ichihara, Chiba|Ichihara, Chiba]], [[:en:Chiba Prefecture|Chiba Prefecture]]) * [[:en:Isohama Kofun Cluster|Isohama Kofun Cluster]] ({{ill|Ōarai, Ibaraki|ja|東茨城郡大洗町|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōarai, Ibaraki|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, [[:en:Ibaraki Prefecture|Ibaraki Prefecture]]) == References == {{Reflist|qq=}} == Bibliography == *{{Cite book|和書|last=広瀬|first=和雄|authorlink=広瀬和雄|editor=公益財団法人{{ill|Kanagawa Archaeology Foundation|ja|かながわ考古学財団|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanagawa Archaeology Foundation|qq=|1=Kanagawa Archeology Foundation|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q30930414}}|title=海浜型前方後円墳の時代|publisher={{ill|Dōsei-sha|ja|同成社|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq